s.n.
</emphasis>
(FI 006937) is here selected as the lectotype of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Labill" authorityYear="1805" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Goodeniaceae" genus="Goodenia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Goodenia repens" order="Asterales" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="repens">
